What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend. The workload is not bad, even though it may seem like it. Classes are usually pretty relaxed and the material is very relevant and up to date.
Recommended if you are interested in current cases of unethical companies, want to learn a theoretical framework for evaluating those companies.
It depends on whether or not you're interested in the class material.
